OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with rain and strong winds
OL,7,Fover Argyll at first spreading
OL,8,Feastwards to all parts. Cloudy with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, becoming
OL,10,Fdrier with clear spells towards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,13,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,14,Fshowers feeding in from the west,
OL,15,Fthese wintry over the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
