OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand very strong winds spreading north
OL,7,Fon Saturday with gales. Blustery
OL,8,Fshowers with winds easing on Sunday.
OL,9,FMostly dry with sunny spells Monday,
OL,10,Fwindy later near coasts.
